WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:03.240
Nicely done, we're in!

2
00:00:03.240 --> 00:00:04.080
Right...

3
00:00:04.080 --> 00:00:07.080
We'll need her memorable word
 to get into her e-mail system.

4
00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:10.960
Looks like she's used a crossword option
 for password reminder.

5
00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:15.640
Hopefully, you'll be able to find that
 crossword and solve it to get access.

6
00:00:15.640 --> 00:00:18.480
Seems to be all about staying safe online.

7
00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:20.640
So if you need any pointers,

8
00:00:20.640 --> 00:00:22.920
I'm sure she's left
 one of our leaflets around somewhere.

9
00:00:23.880 --> 00:00:26.240
When you're in, we'll see
 what we're dealing with.

